生物化學 (一)  Biochemistry (I) (English)








 
 
 
 











課程首頁

	 

本課程是由交通大學生物科技學系暨研究所提供。

	 

	First semester of biochemistry course series. This course focuses on the structures, chemical properties, and function of proteins and enzymes, carbohydrates, lipids, and nucleic acids. Basic enzyme kinetics and catalytic mechanisms.


	(This course is taught in English.)
 


 





授課教師
生物科技學系 蘭宜錚老師



課程學分
3



